# tensorflow-hub is deliberately absent (#491). It only resolved a URL to a local
# cache and then called tf.saved_model.load; the Dockerfile bakes the model in at
# build time, so app.py loads the SavedModel directly. Dropping it also drops the
# runtime pkg_resources import that forced setuptools<81 and blocked the
# CVE-2026-59890 fix (fixed in setuptools 83.0.0).
